This plugin uses only Anthropic-native features available to Claude Code
Pro/Max/Team/Enterprise subscribers:

  - Claude Opus 4.7 (claude-opus-4-7)
  - Claude Managed Agents (managed-agents-2026-04-01)
  - Anthropic Memory Tool (memory_20250818)
  - Context Editing (context-management-2025-06-27)
  - Compaction (compact_20260112)
  - Task Budgets (task-budgets-2026-03-13)
  - Prompt Caching with 1-hour TTL
  - Batch API
  - Fine-grained Tool Streaming
  - Claude Design (research preview)

No third-party service dependencies.
